Print Premier League Table.

Source: R/pl-table.R
pl_table.Rd

This function prints a table with Premier League teams' performance data, including the number of matches played, wins, draws, losses and points.

Usage

pl_table()

Value

A gt table object displaying the Premier League table.

Examples
